              <h2 className="serif text-4xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-tight">
                Reading made <br/><span className="text-amber-500 italic">effortless.</span>
              </h2>
              <p className="text-stone-500 text-base md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
                Transform any document or web page into a high-quality narrated experience. No servers, no tracking, just pure sound.
